---
layout: layouts/base.njk

blender_url: https://www.blender.org/
wg_url: https://www.watchguard.com/

---

<article class="container mx-auto p-4 md:p-8 text-lg">
  <section class="grid gap-4 md:gap-8 mb-8 md:mb-16">
    <img src="/images/justin_carlson.svg" alt="{{ site.title }}" class="h-10 md:h-14">
    <p class="mb-8">
      Probably cultivating code<sup class="link"><a href="#software">[1]</a></sup> or lost in 3D space<sup class="link"><a href="#art">[2]</a></sup>.
    </p>
  </section>
  <div class="grid gap-16 md:gap-24">
    <section id="software" class="card">
      <h1 class="text-2xl mb-2 font-serif font-bold">1. Software</h1>
      <p class="mb-8">
        I'm currently a Senior Software Engineer at <a class="link" href="{{ wg_url }}">WatchGuard Technologies</a>.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4">
        {% for s in [socials.github, socials.linkedin] %}
        <a href="{{ s.url }}" class="button text-lg font-bold">
          <i class="{{ s.icon }} fa-lg pr-1"></i>
          {{ s.label }}
        </a>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </section>
    <section id="art" class="card">
      <h1 class="text-2xl mb-2 font-serif font-bold">2. Art</h1>
      </h1>
      <p class="mb-8">
        I'm an experienced amateur 3D artist and <a class="link" href="{{ blender_url }}">Blender</a> enthusiast.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4">
        {% for a in [art.neon_ride] %}
        <a href="{{ a.url }}" class="group transform hover:scale-110 transition">
          <img src="{{ a.image }}" alt="{{ a.title }}" class="w-full md:w-80 rounded-lg shadow group-hover:shadow-lg transition">
          <div class="pt-1 text-sm"><i>{{ a.title }}</i>, {{ a.year }}</div>
        </a>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </section>
    <section id="contact" class="card">
      <h1 class="text-2xl mb-2 font-serif font-bold">3. Contact</h1>
      <p class="mb-8">
        Lick a virtual envelope and send it to <a class="link" href="{{ socials.email.url }}">{{ socials.email.label }}</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</article>
